"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]宇文玉的手有些微微颤抖，但很快就镇定下来，似乎是在做一件做过很多次的事情一般。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]拿起眉笔，轻轻在\\n[1]脸上画起来。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]想着这样结束后，说自己看上这个舞女，好带着\\n[1]离开，这样那些要告诉她的事情，一定要告诉给她。"]},{"code":231,"indent":0,"parameters":[1,"11-YNZYH3",0,0,0,0,100,100,255,0]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]\\n[1]心情复杂，对于宇文一家，她本应该赶尽杀绝，却不知道为什么。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]她总感觉宇文玉有些熟悉感，但是说不出来为什么会有这样的感觉。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]像是做一件很平常的事情，明明给女子画眉，也是表达自己的喜欢的意思。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]王太傅看着一脸迷茫的\\n[1]，又看了看宇文玉，想起了宇文卿干的事情，立马说身体不适停止了宴会。"]},{"code":101,"indent":0,"parameters":["",0,1,2,""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":[""]},{"code":401,"indent":0,"parameters":["\\CT[1]抓着\\n[1]说要单独犒赏，宇文玉不好当面反对，只能点头离开。"]},{"code":235,"indent":0,"parameters":[1]},{"code":221,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":122,"indent":0,"parameters":[524,524,0,0,1]},{"code":201,"indent":0,"parameters":[0,109,43,14,2,0]},{"code":211,"indent":0,"parameters":[1]},{"code":117,"indent":0,"parameters":[116]},{"code":222,"indent":0,"parameters":[]},{"code":0,"indent":0,"parameters":[]}],"moveFrequency":3,"moveRoute":{"list":[{"code":0,"parameters":[]}],"repeat":true,"skippable":false,"wait":false},"moveSpeed":3,"moveType":0,"priorityType":0,"stepAnime":false,"through":false,"trigger":